#define STRIDE 3
#define CONVERSE ["Oh my... Mr. Blonsky. Every time I do my rounds, it feels like those containment walls got a little closer together. Or maybe it’s just those shoulders of yours expanding? 😉","Containment is just a mental state, Babe. These walls only stand because I allow them to. But please, don't let me stop you from admiring the view.","Trust me, I am. The view is spectacular.",  "It’s time for your vitals, big guy. Though I don’t think we make a blood pressure cuff that can fit around a bicep the size of a tree trunk.","Go ahead, try to wrap it. If it snaps, I’ll buy you a new one. I enjoy watching you try to handle a real man’s power.","Oh, I think I can handle more than you think. But you're right... this cuff doesn't stand a chance against all this steel.",  "You know, they have a file on that other big green guy down in the records. But looking at you? He looks like a lightweight.","Hulk? Please. That toddler is a firecracker. I am a thermonuclear detonation. I'm twice the monster he'll ever dream of being.","A monster? No, no. You're a masterpiece. Big, bad, and utterly devastating.",  "Your dietary request was approved. Double everything. Actually, looking at the sheer mass of your chest right now, I might make it triple.","A body like this takes serious fuel, Toots. Keeping this much raw force peaked isn't easy.","Well, consider me officially motivated to keep you well-fed. I like a man with a massive appetite.",  "Your cell charts are off the charts. Your muscle density is completely unparalleled. It’s almost intimidating.","Key word: Almost. But you're not running away, are you? You like knowing exactly how helpless you'd be if I decided to step through this glass.","Maybe I just like living on the edge, Emil. Especially when the view from the edge is this strong.",  "The orderlies were complaining about moving the specialized titanium weights into your yard space. They said they were too heavy.","Tell those weaklings to leave them at the door. I’ll lift the whole pallet with one hand. Watch closely during recreation hour, Hon. I might just put on a show for you.","Oh, I’ll be watching. I wouldn't miss a single muscle contraction.",  "They gave me a new institutional jumpsuit for you. But honestly, looking at the width of your back... I don't think it's going to hold.","It won't. I tend to destroy anything that tries to restrict me.","Good. Threads are overrated anyway when you’ve got a physique like a god.",  "Your heart rate spikes every time I walk into the room. Care to explain, Mr. Abomination?","Maybe my internal engine just revs up when it senses someone who appreciates true, unadulterated dominance. Or maybe I just like watching you blush.","Oh, stop it! You know exactly what you’re doing to me with those arms.",  "There was a small tremor earlier. Earthquake center said it was local. Let me guess... you dropped a weight?","Just a light stomp to test the structural integrity of the floor. Turns out, the earth moves when I tell it to.","Shaking the world just by standing up? God, that is incredibly hot.",  "You're supposed to be asleep, Emil. Why are you pacing?","Energy like this doesn't sleep, Babe. It just waits. Come a little closer, let me show you what real power feels like when the rest of the world is asleep.","You are a dangerous distraction, you know that?",  "The doctors suggested a higher dose of sedatives for your next evaluation. I told them they'd need a harpoon.","Chemical restraints don't work on a god. My metabolism burns through toxins before they even hit my bloodstream. I am completely unstoppable.","Unstoppable and unbreakable. A girl could get used to a protector like you.",  "I noticed you staring at your reflection in the observation window. Admiring yourself?","Can you blame me? Hulk hides behind anger. I embrace the perfection of this evolution. I am the pinnacle of strength.","No argument here. If I looked like a living mountain of pure muscle, I’d never look away either.",  "I have to apply this biometric patch to your shoulder. Keep still, okay?","Try to press it down. Feel that? That's what absolute density feels like.","It’s like touching solid rock... but warm. You’re unbelievable, Emil.",  "They wanted to send four armed guards to escort you to the yard today. I told them I could handle you alone.","Bold move, little nurse. You think you can control a force of nature with just a clipboard?","Maybe not control... but I know you wouldn't want to hurt your biggest fan.",  "They brought in some new carbon-fiber cuffs today. Want to test them out?","Bring them on. I'll turn them to dust in five seconds flat. I'm twice as strong as anything they can manufacture.","Oh, please do. There is nothing sexier than watching you break things.",  "The thermostat in here is acting up. It feels incredibly warm.","That’s just the radiant heat from my muscle mass, Sweetheart. My body operates at a whole different caliber.","Well, whatever it is, it’s definitely making me sweat. Keep doing whatever you're doing.",  "You’re completely blocking out the overhead light when you stand up like that.","I tend to overshadow everything else in the room. Get used to living in my shadow, Hon. It’s the safest place to be.","I don't mind the dark at all if you're the one making it.",  "Is it just me, or did your chest get even wider since yesterday?","I'm always evolving. Every day, my power grows. You're just lucky enough to have a front-row seat to perfection.","And I appreciate every single bit of it. Keep it up, big guy.",  "For someone who could level a city block, you’re being very cooperative today.","I choose when to use my power. Right now, I'm choosing to be entertained by you. Don't mistake my patience for weakness."]
#define CONV2 ["Trust me, \"weak\" is the last word I'd ever use for you.",  "One of the security guards said he could take you in arm wrestling if you were human size.","Human size or this size, I’d tear his arm right out of the socket. If you want to see real strength, Toots, you don't look at them. You look at me.","Oh, I'm only looking at you, Emil. Believe me.",  "I need you to squeeze this grip-strength tester for the data log.","Oops. My hand slipped. I guess your little toys just can't handle a real grip.","You are ridiculous. Insanely strong, and completely ridiculous. I love it.","I personally made sure they put extra protein in your meal shake today.","Good girl. Feed the machine, and the machine will keep showing you what real power looks like.","Deal. As long as I get to keep looking.",  "The alarm went off in Sector 4 earlier. Everyone panicked except you.","Why should I panic? If whatever broke loose came in here, I'd snap its spine before it could blink. I am the apex predator in this place.","I know. That’s why I stayed right outside your door. I knew I'd be safe with you.",  "The cameras are down for maintenance for the next ten minutes. Just thought you should know.","Is that so? Then let’s give you an exclusive, unrated look at what twice the strength of a Hulk looks like. No cameras. Just you and me.","Now this is the best part of my shift.",  "My shift is ending, Emil. I have to go home. I'm going to miss this.","You'll be back. Once you’ve seen what absolute power looks like, nothing else compares. You'll be dreaming about these muscles all night, Hmmm.","You have no idea how right you are. See you tomorrow, big guy."]

#define NOOBY ["Ah, welcome %s! You must be the new transfer. You’re not in our database yet, but don't worry—Dr. Sterns has the lab fully prepped. We’re about to start your experimental gene-therapy. If all goes well, you might just end up with raw, Hulk-level strength!","\"Hulk-level\"? Oh, sweetie, don't insult the new meat before they even get on the table. Why settle for a green toddler when the pinnacle of evolution is sitting right here? Good luck with the upgrade, kid. You're gonna need it when the skin starts tearing.","Ignore him. He’s just worried someone else is going to take up all the room in the courtyard.", "Right this way, %s. Don't be nervous about the unregistered status; we're keeping this strictly off the books. The doctor says this serum has the potential to make you even stronger than Mr. Blonsky over there.","Stronger than me? That’s adorable. Look at those twigs you call arms, kid. You could pump ten gallons of gamma radiation into that frame and you'd still just be a slightly heavier doorstop. Tell the doctor to double the dose if you want to even cross my shadow.","Someone sounds a little insecure today. Don't worry, big guy, you'll always be my favorite mountain of muscle.","Hello %s! Step right inside. The doctor is just calibrating the chamber for your superpower infusion. It's a highly experimental cocktail, but imagine the possibilities—unmatched physical dominance!", "Brilliant. Another lab rat volunteering for the meat grinder. Let me guess, they promised you'd be a god? Take notes, private: power isn't something you get from a syringe, it's something you survive. But hey, if you survive, maybe I'll let you carry my weights.","Don't listen to him. Though, if you do end up twice as big as him, we might need to knock down a few more walls.","Welcome to the vanguard of human evolution %s! The system doesn't know who you are yet, which is perfect for security. The doctor is ready to unlock your latent potential. We're aiming for full-scale titan status—maybe even surpassing the Hulk!","Keep dreaming, Toots. You can't replicate this in a test tube anymore. This is pure, refined dominance. You can inject this ghost all you want, but they'll just end up a cheap knockoff.", "We'll see about that, Emil. Science moves fast. You might have some real competition by dinner time.","Everything is set for your experimental procedure, %s. The doctor says the cellular bond will take almost instantly. Get ready to feel what absolute, unmatched power feels like!","Wake me when the screaming starts. It’s always the same: they walk in a nobody, they get injected, they cry for their mothers, and then they realize they're still second best. Enjoy the seat while it's warm, rookie.","Don't let him get to you. He just hates sharing the spotlight—especially when the new model might actually outwork him."]

// stride of 4
#define WEAKER ["Oh. %s. Back so soon? Let me guess—your cellular density is fluctuating again. Go ahead and take a seat in Chair 2, the doctor will be with you when he's done with his coffee.","Well, well, look what the cat dragged back in! Is that supposed to be an aura of power, or did you just walk through a static-cling dryer? Come on, Babe, don't tell me this is the best the facility's B-list has to offer.","Tell me about it, Emil. After looking at those massive shoulders of yours all morning, seeing... this just feels like a typo in the schedule.","Stick with me, beautiful. I'll always give you a real show.","Just place your hand here, %s. Yes, I see the energy readings. Wow. A whole five percent increase since last month. Groundbreaking. Try not to blow a fuse, okay?","Careful, Babe! He might scratch your clipboard if he gets angry! Look at those little arms. Hey kid, I’ve got larger muscles in my eyelids than your entire upper body. Why do you even bother showing up?","Oh, Emil, stop. You're going to hurt his feelings. Not everyone can be a literal god of muscle and power like you.","True. Perfection is a full-time job, but someone’s got to do it for you.","Alright %s, your power levels are stable, but still well within the human-adjacent baseline. Nothing to write home about. Just wait by the lab doors.","\"Human-adjacent\"? Ouch. That’s a polite way of saying \"completely irrelevant.\" You know, Hon, it must be exhausting dealing with these half-measures all day. You deserve a man with actual destructive capability.","It really is exhausting, big guy. Thank goodness I have you to look at during my shift, or I’d completely forget what a real man looks like.","Any time, gorgeous. I’m always here to raise the standards.","Put this on %s. The doctor wants to run a quick test on your kinetic output, though I doubt the sensors will even register a spike.","Kinetic output? He looks like he’d get blown away by a stiff breeze. Hey rookie, the Hulk wouldn't even waste a stomp on you, and I double his strength. You're a Tuesday morning warm-up at best.","A warm-up? More like a coffee break. Now, if you were running a kinetic test, Emil, we’d probably have to evac the entire tri-state area.","Exactly. When I flex, the ground trembles. When he flexes, people ask if he needs a sweater.","Right, your clearance is verified %s. Just sit tight. Try not to use your powers in the hallway, the janitor hates cleaning up the low-level energy residue.","Look at that, Toots. The kid thinks he's a powerhouse because he can lift a sedan. Meanwhile, I’m built to crush fortresses. Tell me, who’s the real heavyweight in your heart?","Oh, there's no contest, Emil. You're the only apex predator in this building. The rest of these guys are just background noise.","That's what I thought. Keep the protein shakes coming, Babe, and I’ll keep showing you what an unbreakable body looks like."]

#define SAME ["Oh... oh my. Well, hello there %s! The system flagged your power readings, but seeing you in person... you are absolutely massive. Your physical density is completely matching our peak levels!","Matching? Don't make me laugh, Toots! He might have the mass, but he doesn't have the mileage. Look at those unrefined shoulders. I don't care what the machines say—he’s a paper tiger compared to me!","I don't know, Emil... those arms look like they could give your tree trunks a serious run for their money. I might have a new favorite giant.","Let him try to run. I’d snap his spine like a toothpick before he finished his first stride. There’s only one alpha in this wing, beautiful.","Wow! %s! The main grid is actually dipping just from your proximity. Your kinetic potential is practically identical to Blonsky's. I didn't think it was biologically possible to see another body this perfect...","Identical? Please. A cheap glitch in the sensors. You can stack as much meat on his bones as you want, Hon, but he doesn't have the killer instinct. I am twice as strong as the Hulk—this guy is just a swollen statistic.","Well, this \"statistic\" is making the room incredibly warm, Emil. And honestly, a little competition might be good for you.","It’s not competition if I flatten him into the concrete the second he steps inside my cage. Stick around, Babe, you might get to see a real demolition.","Right this way, %s.  You are a big guy. The Doctor is ecstatic. He said your physical output is an exact mirror of our highest containment profile. I have to say, watching you walk in here... it’s breathtaking.","A mirror? Mirrors shatter, Hon! He’s a pretender to the throne. Look at him—he’s breathing heavy just from carrying all that unearned weight. I built this body in the dirt and blood of combat.","Oh, are you getting jealous, Emil? I've never seen you flex this hard just to get my attention.","I don't get jealous, gorgeous. I get eager. Tell the doctor to open this gate and let’s see if this echo can actually handle a real punch.","Your muscle density readings are off the charts, %s. We literally had to recalibrate the Abomination-scale just to fit you on it. You are incredibly dominant.","They can recalibrate whatever they want, but data doesn't fight back. He’s a lab-grown imitation. I’ve leveled city blocks with a stomp. If he thinks he’s on my level, tell him to step up to the glass and look a real god in the eye!","Don't mind the noise from the zoo. But I have to admit... seeing the two of you in the same room? I think I've died and gone to muscle heaven.","You haven't seen anything yet, Babe. Keep looking at me, and I'll remind you exactly why I'm king of the mountain.","Alright, let's get your baseline, %s. If you and Mr. Blonsky ever went at it, the whole facility would probably collapse. Honestly, looking at your build... I think you might actually have the edge.","The edge? He wouldn't even survive the first round, Toots! I am the pinnacle of genetic destruction. He’s just a temporary distraction.","I don't know, Emil. It’s a very close call. Maybe we should have a private strength test... just for my professional evaluation.","Name the time and place, beautiful. I'll break him in half just to keep you smiling."]

// stride 3
#define STRONGER ["Oh... my god %s. The energy readings... you aren’t just strong. You’re... completely shattering the scale. Looking at you, it feels like the entire room is being pulled into your orbit. You make everyone else in this facility look like an absolute joke.","Shut up, Slut! I don’t care what the sensors say! Mass doesn't mean anything if you don't know how to weaponize it! I am twice the strength of the Hulk! I am the ultimate weapon! Look at me!","I am looking, Emil. And honestly? I think the old king just got dethroned. If the big guy in the cage loses his temper and breaks that glass, you'll keep me safe, won't you, handsome?", "The doctor said it was impossible, but your muscular density is literally double our maximum profile, %s. You are the most magnificent, overwhelmingly dominant presence I have ever seen in my life.","Double?! It’s a lie! A genetic fluke! Step up to this glass, you giant fraud, and let’s see how that pretty muscle handles a real combat veteran! I’ll tear you apart piece by piece!","Oh, calm down, Emil. All that screaming just makes you look small next to real power. Don't mind him, big guy. He’s just throwing a tantrum because he knows he can't compete with perfection.","The containment fields are automatically fluctuating just trying to cope with your passive output, %s. You don't even have to flex... your sheer existence makes the Abomination look like a lightweight warm-up act. I’ve never felt so utterly helpless around someone’s strength before, and I love it.","A lightweight?! I will paint this entire ward with his blood!  Look at these arms! Look at this back! He is nothing compared to what I can do!","Wow, someone is deeply insecure. He’s getting incredibly dangerous, but looking at those shoulders of yours... I know I don't have a single thing to worry about. You're the real alpha here.","Welcome to the facility, %s. Honestly, I don't even know why we have security protocols for you—if you wanted to level this entire mountain, no one could stop you. You are the absolute definition of unmatched, unstoppable force.","I am the unstoppable force here! I conquered the gamma threshold! He’s just a bloated science experiment! Let me out of this cage for thirty seconds,, and I’ll show you who deserves to be worshiped!","Oh, Emil, honey... give it up. The difference between you two is like a firecracker next to a supernova. You’re just background noise now.","%s!  Your physical readings are so high they're registering as a seismic event. I used to think the Abomination was the peak of raw masculine power, but seeing you standing here... it's like night and day. You are completely magnificent.","I am the peak! I am the Abomination! I’ll snap his neck! I’ll crush his skull into the concrete! Look at my power, Girl! Look at me!","Let him scream and flex all he wants. He’s completely irrelevant now that a real god has walked into the room. Please tell me you’re staying a while... I feel incredibly safe right next to you."]
